	<h1 class="title">听说中国这个冬季流行毛毛鞋，这真的是“时尚”吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">叶芳妤</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-14 18:38:02 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20671/medium/20671.jpg?1452678792" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


